org.jetel.ctl

Interface SyntheticNodeVisitor

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    TransformLangParserVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ASTBuilder, CodePieceExtractor.PositionedCodeVisitor, CTLTransformUtils.CtlAssignmentFinder, FindFunctionVisitor, GetValueFunctionBodyVisitor, NavigatingVisitor, TransformLangExecutor, TranslatingVisitor, TypeChecker

    public interface SyntheticNodeVisitor
    Interface defines visit methods for synthetic AST nodes. I.e. AST nodes that are not generated directly by the parser but by additional compiler phases
